Your shoulder flaring?
Nope.

6
00:03:47,216 --> 00:03:50,208
- You winced.
- I didn't wince.

7
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:52,220
You grimaced.

8
00:03:53,289 --> 00:03:55,450
My shoulder
doesn't hurt, Gus.

9
00:03:55,558 --> 00:03:57,458
[ Beeping ]

10
00:04:01,597 --> 00:04:03,462
How long has it
been hurting?

11
00:04:07,303 --> 00:04:09,203
Perry wants me
to start tomorrow.

12
00:04:10,473 --> 00:04:12,373
You gotta be kidding.

13
00:04:14,310 --> 00:04:16,437
You're not doin' it.
No way.

14
00:04:16,546 --> 00:04:18,446
It's the end
of a shitty season.

15
00:04:18,548 --> 00:04:21,210
[ Sighs ]
I'm gonna go talk to Perry.

16
00:04:21,317 --> 00:04:24,343
Sit down.
Sit down. Relax.

17
00:04:24,454 --> 00:04:27,446
Sir, your drink.
Hi.

18
00:04:27,557 --> 00:04:32,392
Thank you.
It's a throwaway, Billy.
It means nothing.

19
00:04:32,495 --> 00:04:34,395
Not to the Red Sox.

20
00:04:36,532 --> 00:04:39,626
If I see you wince
even one time--

21
00:04:39,736 --> 00:04:41,636
Oh, God !

22
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:44,932
[ Chuckles ]
I've--

23
00:04:45,041 --> 00:04:47,305
I've got the ugliest wife
in the league.

24
00:04:49,946 --> 00:04:52,437
That hurts.
It hurt my feeling.

25
00:04:55,051 --> 00:04:57,417
[ Sighs ]
Buckle your seat belt.

