1147
01:26:18,875 --> 01:26:21,105
If it gets any worse,
I'll sit down.

1148
01:26:22,912 --> 01:26:25,107
Ready to go?

1149
01:26:31,287 --> 01:26:33,187
Where's my pat?

1150
01:26:36,392 --> 01:26:38,292
[ Pats ]
Thank you.

1151
01:26:38,394 --> 01:26:41,022
You let me know.
Yeah.
He's all right.

1152
01:26:42,665 --> 01:26:44,724
[ Jane ]
He's flexing his hand.

1153
01:26:44,834 --> 01:26:48,497
What?
He does that when
his arm's tingling.

1154
01:26:48,604 --> 01:26:51,664
Pretty soon he's not gonna
be able to feel anything.
Do you know him?

1155
01:26:53,843 --> 01:26:55,970
Yeah, and I know
Mickey fuckin' Mantle.

1156
01:26:56,078 --> 01:26:58,478
[ Bartender ]
Hey, watch the language.
There's people in here.

1157
01:26:58,581 --> 01:27:01,072
[ Patrons..Mocking Laughter ]
[ Man On P.A.] This is
